      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOAKI RADAR (5) failed to come into contention last start after being shuffled back early at this track, but prior to that won by 0.8 lengths at this track (16.79) beating Ales And Nails in a P5 on July 6. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Ready to return to form. ALTONA BEACH (2) was popular in betting last start but disappointed when 5.5 lengths away in fourth (19.41). Finished third the start before. The form out of her last race has been franked. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PSYCHO SUSIE (1) resumed in a Grade 5 at this track and finished fifth over 300m (17.04). Will strip fitter for the run. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. UNPAID DEBT (7) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
